The paper also discusses recursion and its limitations, which suggests that it may belong to the sub-category of programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also discusses the sizes of values of expressions, which suggests that it may belong to the sub-category of data structures (cs.DS). Finally, the paper's title "Adventures in Time and Space" suggests that it may belong to the sub-category of logic in computer science (cs.LO), which often deals with temporal and spatial reasoning.
